  "text": "Weaponization is an essential step to increase success of an attack by reducing opportunities for attack detection and limiting forensics investigators abilities to analyse detected threats [CITATION_1] . Banking Trojans are employing variety of techniques to disguise detection on host-level and network-level and defeat cyber investigators.",
